<!--Slider-->
<div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
    <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
            aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1"
            aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2"
            aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/images/slider.jpg" class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="Slider 01" />
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h1>Cuidado de mascotas</h1>
                <p>Deja en manos de una persona altamente capacitada.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/slider2.jpg" class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="Slider 02" />
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h1>Tu mascota feliz</h1>
                <p>Proteje el bienestar de tu mascota en todas partes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/slider3.jpg" class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="Slider 03" />
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h1>Necesidades básicas</h1>
                <p>Siempre debemos estar atentos a las diferentes necesidades de nuestras mascotas.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
    </button>
</div>

